    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/0ede9fe8c9e85808bbaa71c745648f57.poster.avif?t=1768157722\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/0ede9fe8c9e85808bbaa71c745648f57.webm?t=1768157722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/0ede9fe8c9e85808bbaa71c745648f57.mp4?t=1768157722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《林间小世界》是一款休闲、治愈的城堡建造小游戏。不用管理，不用战斗，没有对错，随心建造城堡，把被人遗忘的草地变成可爱的微缩景观。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/bcb9fcfc127a7ba044ae146a09b6fd40.webp?t=1768157722\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/593176b1e4efdcf2f039178c30d2d67f.poster.avif?t=1768157722\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/593176b1e4efdcf2f039178c30d2d67f.webm?t=1768157722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/593176b1e4efdcf2f039178c30d2d67f.mp4?t=1768157722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>(没有网格限制)<br><br>本作没有网格限制，玩家可以尽情探索建筑材料的互动，看游戏能用砖头、石块、木板搭出怎样的天地。画了一条穿墙的路？墙上就会开出一道拱门！想让拱门宽一点？柱子就会立起来。把墙往下压一压？拱门就会变成篱笆和普通的门。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/330883cd133ed97b58bfd2077dad78c5.webp?t=1768157722\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/4ea47d0500dec48ebd98e6879f028658.poster.avif?t=1768157722\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/4ea47d0500dec48ebd98e6879f028658.webm?t=1768157722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/4ea47d0500dec48ebd98e6879f028658.mp4?t=1768157722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>(没有对错)<br><br>无所谓对和错，也没有失败，随时都可以换设计思路，不论怎么搭建，城堡都会非常可爱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/fef3ee6b07bef9b9de0f13691124337d.webp?t=1768157722\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/40d007115af739446f074011fb3ebc88.poster.avif?t=1768157722\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/40d007115af739446f074011fb3ebc88.webm?t=1768157722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198150/extras/40d007115af739446f074011fb3ebc88.mp4?t=1768157722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>(气氛闲适)<br><br>游戏气氛闲适，小小天地供你回避忧虑和烦扰。藤蔓爬上了墙壁，绵羊慢悠悠地走着，夜晚还能看到成群的萤火虫。",
